blog.name: solardanvers
blog.title: Higher, Further, Faster, Baby
blog.description: Welcome to the writing prompt blog of starryystark! Request fics for MCU including Tony Stark, Pepper Potts, Peter Parker, Natasha Romanoff, T'Challa, Shuri, probably anyone! Open to intense subjects, sm*t on case-by-cause basis. Not my icon!

title: Takes Prompt Requests!
body:
Hey! I’m actually a side blog of @starryystark  ‘s that will be doing prompt requests for fics, drabbles, etc. ! Down below will be things i will and wont write, but im open to a lot of stuff as in subject, not so much fandom! I’d appreciate if you take the time to check out my main blog as well and my a03! Hope you request soon!

THINGS I WILL BE WILLING TO WRITE:

  • MCU ONLY (Sorry, maybe I’ll open it up to Star Trek, Doctor Who, and Star Wars if I get inspiration : ( ) 
  • Tony Stark, Steve Rogers, Natasha Romanoff, Pepper Potts, Peter Parker, Thor, Shuri, T’Challa, pretty much ANY MCU character you can think of I’ll probably write for!
  • Lengths can be of any length, honestly, 500 words or 10,000 i can do any day! 
  • I am willing to write intense subjects including depression, drinking, self harm, suicide, abuse, r*pe, anything in the book, theres only minimal chance ill turn you down because your request is too intense
  • Fluff, of course
  • Lovey-dovey (or, well, just romance) 
  • Comedy (DUH)
  • Full length fic (3K+ words)
  • Series (maybe….depends on how good it sounds : )  ) 
  • Drabbles!
  • Hurt/Comfort
  • Emotional
  • Spoiler stories
  • Stories taking place in or after A4, Spiderman: Far From Home, etc. 
  • OCs! OCs are valid and appreciated! If you like you can DM me a profile or summary for your OC so I can nail the character right!
  • Reader inserts (as growingly unpopular as they seem to me? Is that just me?) 
  • I’m always open to writing trades or tumblr activities and such so if you see something and think of me, thats totally appreciated!

THINGS I WILL NOT BE WILLING TO WRITE: 

  • MCU does not include Jessica Jones, Daredevil, or any Netflix Marvel shows, and does not include Runaways or any Hulu Marvel show
  • Non-MCU fandoms (may change in future) 
  • I may write smut on case-by-case basis but probably not. May change in the future may not change idk
